  <brief_title>Titanium Elastic Nailing Versus Hip Spica Cast in Treatment of Femoral Fractures in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Surgical Method Versus Casting for Treatment of Femoral Fracture in Children</official_title>
  <sponsors>
