  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients 6-12 years old with femoral shaft fracture without exclusion criteria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Segmental, Winquist type III and IV comminuted fractures, previously diagnosed
             neuromuscular disease (e.g., cerebral palsy), metabolic bone disorders (e.g.
             osteomalacia), or pathological fractures.
      </textblock>
